0.8.4.name: wordpress/jquery-mobile
0.8.4.description:
This plugin installs the jQuery Mobile framework, which is based on jQuery and jQuery UI.

It`s recommended to use this plugin together with my jQuery updater plugin for javascript compatibility. WordPress 3.2+ is a requirement! This plugin should not work with WordPress versions lower than 3.2 because jQuery 1.6+ is required.
